  <lyrics>[V1]
 Kota taypin utjatayna
 Suma achunaca, suma evangelio
 Yatichirinaca, munasiñ arinac
 Khanañchirinaca. (bis)
 
[V2]
 CORO
 Yatichitay arunacamata
 Chuymajjaru munasiñ churita
 Cawquirusa jumajj irpitata
 Jumar jaysir nayar tuct’ayita. (bis)
 
 
[V3]
 Cawqui chekans utjapiniw
 Wawanacamajja irpitay Awquejja
 Jumat khanañchiri,
 Junac’ac jutawimat yatiyañataqui. (bis)
 
[V4]
 Kollanapjjew arunacap
 Yatiyirinacajj, jupanacanquiwa
 Alajjpach marcajja,
 Cawquirus irpistpan jan’ac sarañani. (bis)
 </lyrics></song>